%% Connection flowchart
flowchart TD
  subgraph Client[Logistics_StockLevel]
    C1[Logistics_FleetManagement]
    C2[Logistics_TrackingNumber]
    C3[Logistics_TrackingNumber]
    C4[Logistics_TrackingNumber]
    C5[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
  end

  subgraph Server[Logistics_Warehouse]
    S1[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
    S2{Logistics_DeliveryRoute}
    S3[Logistics_FleetManagement]
    S4[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
    S5[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
    S6[Logistics_TrackingNumber]
  end

  C1 --> C2 --> C3 --> S1
  S1 -->|invalid| Drop[Logistics_Warehouse]
  S1 --> S2
  S2 -- yes --> S3 --> S4 --> C5
  S2 -- no --> S5

  C5 -- piggyback --> S1
  C5 -- no_outgoing --> ExplicitACK[Logistics_FleetManagement] --> S1
  C4 --> C3

  S6 --> Close[Logistics_FleetManagement]
